**MindMate** is an AI-powered mental wellness companion built for the Lyzr AI Architect Challenge. It helps users reflect on their emotions, offers empathetic responses, and suggests journaling or mindfulness activities based on principles from Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT) and positive psychology.

